<br>
Bistia , sorry for the yer fail on Tal today but it was ur owen fault . I offerd the help from DD members to kill em with ur guild then i saw u didnt got enough ppl on for em to try em successfull and we was ready to take em down . <br>
I think also my offer about we could share the loot was more then nice so i dont understand why u didnt accept our help and tryed em with ur owen ppl .<br>
After ur guild failed on em u send me a tell if i could bring ppl to help to try em again with our help , but my guildis didnt accept ur offer now , understandable or ?<br>
Ur guild left Sf after the CR , DD formed up and killed Tal , and he dropped a red Scale what could be urs then that was a part of the deal i offerd u and im sure u would also earn it , but so a member from DD earned it .<br>
btw it was almost the worsest loot ever on Tal beside the red Scale . he droped a pos bard Drum , GoFM , pos bracer and 4 spells ( thanx verant ).<br>
<br>
Note : Its isnt bad or wrong to accept the offer and help from a other guild to kill a mob or getting help to do anything , but I think its the 'Ego' in Everyone ( like lewen or any other bards on all server around the world , p ) what say 'NO we dont need help' . But thats the wrong way i think . DD also killed Sev on Monday with TA and FA members without any problems ( beside the first whipeout ,p ) and a month before with unity and we had fun . I think we all should work together and not against then this is only a game where we should have fun . the RL sux more then enough so we should be cool and nice in game <br>
<br>
I wish IV more luck on the next attempt on tal or any other mob <br>
<br>
This is only my opinion and not of my guild or any members from DD<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
                        Daimien Angellight<br>
                       Crusader of Karana<br>
                Proud Member of Domus Divinae<br>
