<br>
There was nothing &quot;ego&quot; related in our decision as most of us have asked and received help in the past from other guilds on plane raids and the like. It was just a decision to move on.<br>
<br>
Fact is we didnt have enough people there and I knew it when I entered the zone. 6 groups 57-60 with high resists is preferred and we only had about 20 55+ with around 10 52-54 people as well. But we did want to try, to get a feel for where we are as a guild to fight such things.<br>
<br>
I think many that participated got a good feel for whats needed and we will be better prepared in the future. Thanks to DD and FA for offering their assistance.<br>
<br>
Backalley<br>
60 Roguelett<br>
